## 8. Architecture

```
friday/
  main.py              GUI entry
  background_listener.py   Wake listener daemon
  launcher.py          Launch/focus app
  ipc.py               IPC files
  config.py            Settings
  policy/              Safety
  core/                Router, intents, brain
  ui/                  PySide6 interface
  voice/               STT, TTS, engine
  integrations/        Browser, apps, web APIs
  installer/           PyInstaller
tests/                 Unit tests
```

